Anime is a style of animation that originated in Japan and has become popular worldwide. It covers a wide range of genres and can be aimed at different age groups. Anime often features colorful artwork, fantastical themes, and vibrant characters.

A petty cashbook is a record of small, day-to-day expenses of a business that are paid in cash. It is used to track and manage minor expenses like office supplies, postage, or small repairs. The petty cashbook helps in maintaining transparency and accountability for these small cash transactions within the organization.
